</span>, <span>la</span> <span>coccinelle</span> <span>a</span> <span>6</span> <span>pattes</span>. ||<span>Prenez</span> l''<span>endos</span> d''<span>un</span> <span>gros</span> <span>pinceau</span> <span>et</span> <span>faites</span> <span>des</span> <span>points</span> <span>noirs</span> <span>sur</span> <span>les</span> <span>élytres</span>. ||<span>Ensuite</span>, <span>prenez</span> <span>un</span> <span>pinceau</span> <span>un</span> <span>peu</span> <span>plus</span> <span>mince</span> <span>pour</span> <span>faire</span> <span>des</span> <span>points</span> <span>blancs</span> ||<span>pour</span> <span>représenter</span> <span>les</span> <span>yeux</span>. ||<span>Quand</span> <span>la</span> <span>peinture</span> <span>blanche</span> <span>est</span> <span>sèche</span>, ||<span>vous</span> <span>pouvez</span> <span>rajouter</span> <span>des</span> <span>points</span> <span>noirs</span> <span>si</span> <span>vous</span> <span>voulez</span>. ||<span>Les</span> <span>points</span> <span>noirs</span> <span>représentent</span> <span>les</span> <span>iris</span>; <span>même</span> <span>si</span> <span>ce</span> n''<span>est</span> <span>pas</span> <span>scientifiquement</span> <span>exact</span>, ||<span>ça</span> <span>rend</span> <span>la</span> <span>coccinelle</span> <span>bien</span> <span>sympathique</span>. ||<span>Si</span> <span>vous</span> <span>voulez</span>, <span>vous</span> <span>pouvez</span> <span>également</span> <span>tracer</span> <span>les</span> <span>nervures</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>feuille</span>. ||<span>Il</span> <span>est</span> <span>préférable</span> <span>de</span> <span>ne</span> <span>pas</span> <span>les</span> <span>faire</span> <span>avant</span> <span>de</span> <span>peindre</span> <span>la</span> <span>coccinelle</span> ||<span>car</span> <span>la</span> <span>peinture</span> <span>rouge</span> <span>est</span> <span>souvent</span> <span>transparente</span> ||<span>et</span> <span>les</span> <span>nervures</span> <span>seraient</span> <span>visibles</span> <span>à</span> <span>travers</span> <span>le</span> <span>corps</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>coccinelle</span>. ||<span>Il</span> <span>reste</span> <span>juste</span> <span>à</span> <span>écrire</span> <span>un</span> <span>gentil</span> <span>message</span> <span>à</span> l''<span>intérieur</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>carte</span>. ||<span>Pour</span> <span>imprimer</span> <span>le</span> <span>document</span> <span>avec</span> <span>des</span> <span>instructions</span> <span>illustrées</span> <span>et</span> <span>le</span> <span>patron</span> <span>de</span> <span>la</span> <span>feuille</span>, ||<span>cliquez</span> <span>sur</span> <span>le</span> <span>lien</span> <span>sous</span> <span>la</span> <span>vidéo</span> ||<span>et</span> <span>venez</span> <span>explorer</span> <span>le</span> <span>site</span> d''<span>Animassiettes</span> <span>pour</span> <span>y</span> <span>trouver</span> <span>des</span> <span>tas</span> d''<span>autres</span> <span>idées</span>. ', '', 0, '2016-08-20 18:31:03', NULL, 'faire-une-carte-avec-une-coccinelle', 0, 0, 0, '2016-08-20 16:31:03', '2016-08-20 16:31:03', '0.41,2.77,8.08,13.79,19.57,23.98,29.05,33.7,36.71,44.239,50.64,55.77,61.85,65.47,69.01,72.76,75.61,78.97,83.35,87.07,94.07,97.85,99.35,105.57,110.72,116.68,120.98,124.62,130.28,133.8,137.84,142.43,147.08,152.38,154.88,157.93,159.92,165.43,167.23,173.31,178.29,180.62,184.96,189.29,195.89,197.98', '||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||', 'intermediate', 3, 2, 2, 0, '0Cj_AazWqjE', '');
