(667, 'PEPPA - Le printemps', '', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/a8HkPNTF5p0.jpg', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/a8HkPNTF5p0.mp4', 'http://o9dnc9u2v.bkt.clouddn.com/videos/a8HkPNTF5p0.mp4', '1\r\n00:48:05,382 --> 00:48:07,184\r\n- Je m''appelle Peppa Cochon.\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:48:07,184 --> 00:48:07,617\r\n(grognement)\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:48:07,617 --> 00:48:09,453\r\nLui, c''es mon petit frère,\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:48:09,453 --> 00:48:11,588\r\nGeorge. Et voici maman Cochon.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:48:11,588 --> 00:48:12,522\r\n(grognement)\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:48:12,522 --> 00:48:14,224\r\nEt voilà, papa Cochon.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:48:14,224 --> 00:48:16,293\r\n(grognement et rires)\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:48:16,293 --> 00:48:17,894\r\nPeppa. (grognement)\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:48:17,894 --> 00:48:20,497\r\n(rires)\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:48:20,497 --> 00:48:20,597\r\n- \r\n\r\n11\r\n00:48:20,597 --> 00:48:22,032\r\nC''est le printemps et\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:48:22,032 --> 00:48:23,867\r\ngrand-père Cochon a organisé\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:48:23,867 --> 00:48:25,302\r\nune chasse aux oeufs\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:48:25,302 --> 00:48:25,769\r\nen chocolat.\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:48:25,769 --> 00:48:27,437\r\n- Alors, est-ce que tout\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:48:27,437 --> 00:48:28,505\r\nle monde est prêt?\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:48:28,505 --> 00:48:30,340\r\n- Non, grand-père, Freddy Renard\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:48:30,340 --> 00:48:31,908\r\nn''est pas encore arrivé.\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:48:31,908 --> 00:48:33,477\r\n(klaxon)\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:48:33,477 --> 00:48:34,811\r\n(petits cris de Freddy)\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:48:34,811 --> 00:48:36,446\r\n- Bonjour, les amis.\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:48:36,446 --> 00:48:38,048\r\n(tous): Bonjour, Freddy.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:48:38,048 --> 00:48:40,383\r\nAh. Bonjour, monsieur Renard.\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:48:40,383 --> 00:48:41,918\r\nVoulez-vous rester avec nous?\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:48:41,918 --> 00:48:42,986\r\n- Oh, j''aurais bien voulu.\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:48:42,986 --> 00:48:44,488\r\nJ''adorais chercher des oeufs en\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:48:44,488 --> 00:48:45,655\r\nchocolat quand j''étais petit.\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:48:45,655 --> 00:48:46,823\r\nÀ tout à l''heure, Freddy.\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:48:46,823 --> 00:48:47,824\r\n(petits cris de Freddy)\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:48:47,824 --> 00:48:48,625\r\n- Maintenant, est-ce que vous\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:48:48,625 --> 00:48:50,694\r\nêtes prêts à partir à la chasse\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:48:50,694 --> 00:48:51,428\r\naux oeufs?\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:48:51,428 --> 00:48:53,530\r\n- Oui, grand-père Cochon.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:48:53,530 --> 00:48:55,031\r\n- Avant votre arrivée, j''ai\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:48:55,031 --> 00:48:57,300\r\ncaché dans mon jardin des tas\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:48:57,300 --> 00:48:59,436\r\nd''oeufs en chocolat. À vous\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:48:59,436 --> 00:49:00,670\r\nde les retrouver.\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:49:00,670 --> 00:49:01,805\r\n- Trop facile.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:49:01,805 --> 00:49:02,239\r\n(grognement)\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:49:02,239 --> 00:49:04,441\r\nMais faites attention à ne pas\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:49:04,441 --> 00:49:06,676\r\nmarcher sur mes petits plants de\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:49:06,676 --> 00:49:07,577\r\nlégumes. C''est tellement\r\n\r\n43\r\n00:49:07,577 --> 00:49:08,845\r\npassionnant d''assister à la\r\n\r\n44\r\n00:49:08,845 --> 00:49:10,313\r\nnaissance de ces petits bébés\r\n\r\n45\r\n00:49:10,313 --> 00:49:11,882\r\ndès l''arrivée des beaux jours.\r\n\r\n46\r\n00:49:11,882 --> 00:49:13,650\r\n- On te promet de ne pas marcher\r\n\r\n47\r\n00:49:13,650 --> 00:49:15,452\r\ndessus, grand-père Cochon.\r\n\r\n48\r\n00:49:15,452 --> 00:49:16,820\r\n- Merci beaucoup. Alors\r\n\r\n49\r\n00:49:16,820 --> 00:49:18,321\r\namusez-vous bien.\r\n\r\n50\r\n00:49:18,321 --> 00:49:19,623\r\n(rires)\r\n\r\n51\r\n00:49:19,623 --> 00:49:20,924\r\n- La chasse aux oeufs en\r\n\r\n52\r\n00:49:20,924 --> 00:49:22,759\r\nchocolat de grand-père Cochon\r\n\r\n53\r\n00:49:22,759 --> 00:49:23,226\r\nest ouverte.\r\n\r\n54\r\n00:49:23,226 --> 00:49:24,728\r\n- As-tu le temps de prendre une\r\n\r\n55\r\n00:49:24,728 --> 00:4